msg: Fix FSFS repository corruption on power or network disk failure on Windows:

author: jukka
msg: OAK-822: TypeEditor: Missing validation for mandatory items
Now the presence of *all* mandatory items is only checked
when a new node is being added. Afterwards the "mandatoriness"
of items is only checked when they are being removed.
